# UI build toolchain deps.
/internal/server/ui/node_modules/

# Built UI bundles (hashed JS/CSS/fonts) are generated by `make ui` and are NOT
# committed — they're large and churn on every change. `//go:embed all:static`
# still compiles because static/index.html + the brand SVGs stay tracked; run
# `make ui` (or `make build`, which auto-builds the UI when assets are missing)
# to produce a working UI. A clean clone must `make ui` once before the UI renders.
/internal/server/static/assets/
